snippet `(\}|\]|\)|\|)(b|bb)ig` iAm
``
rv="\\big";
let b=m[2].length;
(b==1)?(rv+="l"):(rv+="gl");
(m[1]=="}")?(rv+="\\{"):(m[1]=="]")?(rv+="["):(m[1]==")")?(rv+="("):(rv+="|");
rv+="$1 \\big";
(b==1)?(rv+="r"):(rv+="gr");
(m[1]=="}")?(rv+="\\\\}"):(rv+=m[1]);
rv+="$0"
``
endsnippet

snippet `(\}|\]|\)|\|)(B|BB|Bb)ig` iAm
``
rv="\\Big";
let b=m[2].length;
(b==1)?(rv+="l"):(rv+="gl");
(m[1]=="}")?(rv+="\\{"):(m[1]=="]")?(rv+="["):(m[1]==")")?(rv+="("):(rv+="|");
rv+="$1 \\Big";
(b==1)?(rv+="r"):(rv+="gr");
(m[1]=="}")?(rv+="\\\\}"):(rv+=m[1]);
rv+="$0"
``
endsnippet

